<ol><li><b>Single number bet:</b> pays 35 to 1. Also called =E2=80=9Cstraig=
ht up.=E2=80=9D</li><li><b>Double number bet:</b> pays 17 to 1. Also called=
 a =E2=80=9Csplit.=E2=80=9D&nbsp;</li><li><b>Three number bet:</b> pays 11 =
to 1. Also called a =E2=80=9Cstreet.=E2=80=9D</li><li><b>Four number bet:</=
b> pays 8 to 1. Also called a =E2=80=9Ccorner bet.=E2=80=9D</li><li><b>Five=
 number bet:</b> pays 6 to 1. Only one specific bet which includes the foll=
owing numbers: 0-00-1-2-3.</li><li><b>Six number bets:</b> pays 5 to 1. Exa=
mple: 7, 8, 9, 10, 11, 12. Also called a =E2=80=9Cline.=E2=80=9D</li><li><b=
>Twelve numbers or dozens:</b> (first, second, third dozen) pays 2 to 1.</l=
i><li><b>Column bet (12 numbers in a row):</b> pays 2 to 1.&nbsp;</li><li><=
b>18 numbers (1-18):</b> pays even money.&nbsp;</li><li><b>18 numbers (19-3=
6):</b> pays even money.&nbsp;</li><li><b>Red or black:</b> pays even money=
.&nbsp;</li><li><b>Odd or even:</b> bets pay even money.</li></ol>

